data.meta_description: Urraca de Portugal was born about 1151., they gave birth to 1 child. She died on October 16, 1188 in Valladolid, Valladolid, Castile and León, Spain. This information is part of Van der Feen/Mendels/Rowe/Hesketh Family Tree by zelah strick on Genealogy Online.
